SELECT * FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] where employeeid = 500717 and isactive= 'Y' order by employeeid, ingestiondate
select * from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[hr_leavers] where pers_no = 500717 

SELECT DISTINCT LEAVING FROM [odw_STAndardised_db].[dbo].[hr_leavers] where expected_from = '2020-08-01T00:00:00.0000000' ORDER BY LEAVING

SELECT DISTINCT expected_from FROM [odw_STAndardised_db].[dbo].[hr_leavers] ORDER BY expected_from

select distinct employmentenddate, employeeid   FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] where isactive= 'Y' order by employeeid

SELECT DISTINCT IngestionDate from [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] order by IngestionDate

SELECT
    employeeid, EmploymentEndDate, COUNT(*)
FROM
     [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim]
WHERE IsActive = 'Y'
GROUP BY
     employeeid, EmploymentEndDate
HAVING 
    COUNT(*) > 1
